# QuantDeck needs NO API keys to run.
# The live FastAPI app sources everything (prices, fundamentals, news, analyst
# data) from Yahoo Finance via yfinance — no key, no rate-limit tier.
#
# The two keys below are OPTIONAL and only used by the retired Streamlit pages
# under pages/ (legacy). Leave them unset unless you're running that old UI.

# Financial Modeling Prep — legacy fundamentals (retired; replaced by yfinance)
# FMP_API_KEY=your_key_here

# NewsAPI — legacy "Smart Suggestions" headlines (retired Streamlit screener)
# NEWSAPI_KEY=your_key_here
